fields.name: David Bowie Print
fields.description: This art print is by Andy Warhol, a leading figure in the Pop Art movement. The print displays David Bowie in sharp, vivid images with a high degree of color accuracy.
fields.side_note: Fits standard A3 frames. Frame is not included.

fields.name: Banana Print
fields.description: This art print is by Andy Warhol, a leading figure in the Pop Art movement. The print displays the banana, an internationally recognized symbol of Warhol and is often used for cover albums.
fields.side_note: Fits standard A3 frames. Frame is not included.

fields.name: Campbell's Soup Print
fields.description: This art print is by Andy Warhol, a leading figure in the Pop Art movement. Many stories say that Warhol's choice to paint soup cans reflected on his own devotion to Campbell's soup as a customer. Robert Indiana once said, “I knew Andy very well. The reason he painted soup cans is that he liked soup.
fields.side_note: Fits standard A3 frames. Frame is not included.

fields.name: Wonder Woman Print
fields.description: Roy Lichtenstein is the second most famous pop art painter in the world, after Andy Warhol. This print of Wonder Woman is one of Lichtenstein's most well-known works.
fields.side_note: Fits standard A3 frames. Frame is not included.

fields.name: We're Not in Kansas Anymore Print
fields.description: Roy Lichtenstein is the second most famous pop art painter in the world, after Andy Warhol. This print is iconic for Lichtenstein's style of work depicting a comic strip scene.
fields.side_note: Fits standard A3 frames. Frame is not included.

fields.name: Pow Print
fields.description: Roy Lichtenstein is the second most famous pop art painter in the world, after Andy Warhol. This print displays a humorous scene in Lichtenstein's famous comic strips.
fields.side_note: Fits standard A3 frames. Frame is not included.

fields.name: Love Print
fields.description: Keith Allen Haring was an American artist whose pop art emerged from the New York City graffiti subculture of the 1980s. Haring is recognized for his exclusive use of black and white, and typical use of primary colors as depicted in this print.
fields.side_note: Fits standard A3 frames. Frame is not included.

fields.name: Widewalls Print
fields.description: Keith Allen Haring was an American artist whose pop art emerged from the New York City graffiti subculture of the 1980s. His animated imagery has become a widely recognized visual language
fields.side_note: Fits standard A3 frames. Frame is not included.

fields.name: Dancing Dog Print
fields.description: Keith Allen Haring was an American artist whose pop art emerged from the New York City graffiti subculture of the 1980s. The Barking Dog, alongside the Radiant Baby, is suggested to be the artist most famous tag.
fields.side_note: Fits standard A3 frames. Frame is not included.

fields.name: Studio View Print
fields.description: David Hockney is considered one of the most influential British artists of the 20th century. This print depicts a studio visualised in a flurry of bright and bold colors.
fields.side_note: Fits standard A3 frames. Frame is not included.

fields.name: Pool Print
fields.description: David Hockney is considered one of the most influential British artists of the 20th century. This print depicts his swimming pool series - an iconic Hockney artwork.

fields.name: Down the Winding Road Print
fields.description: David Hockney is considered one of the most influential British artists of the 20th century. This print depicts a studio visualised in a flurry of bright and bold colors.

fields.name: Sunflower Print
fields.description: Takashi Murakami is a famous Japanese contemporary artist. Murakami's vibrant images flourish with colorfully animated flowers which signify peace and happiness.
fields.side_note: Fits standard A3 frames. Frame is not included.

fields.name: Skulls & Sunflowers Print
fields.description: Takashi Murakami is a famous Japanese contemporary artist. Each figure in this print serves as a symbol of a differing theme. While flowers often signify peace and happiness, skulls are visual triggers of death and mortality.
fields.side_note: Fits standard A3 frames. Frame is not included.

fields.name: Landscape Print
fields.description: Liu Wei is a Chinese artist who excels in various mediums including video, installation, and scupture. This work depicts a unique landscape scene using a wide variety of colors and shapes.
fields.side_note: Fits standard A3 frames. Frame is not included.

fields.name: Love Is The Answer Print
fields.description: Banksy's work grew out of the Bristol underground scene, which involved collaborations between artists and musicians. His works of political and social commentary have appeared on streets, walls, and bridges throughout the world. This print is a colourful reproduction of Banksy ‘Love is the Answer’ with Einstein.
fields.side_note: Fits standard A3 frames. Frame is not included.

fields.name: Flower Thrower Print
fields.description: Banksy's work grew out of the Bristol underground scene, which involved collaborations between artists and musicians. His works of political and social commentary have appeared on streets, walls, and bridges throughout the world. This print is one of his most iconic works, 'Rage, Flower Thrower' often interpreted as being anti-war and a pacifist.
fields.side_note: Fits standard A3 frames. Frame is not included.

fields.name: Man With Crown Print
fields.description: Basquiat is a famous painter known for his raw gestural style of painting with graffiti-like images and scrawled text.With his signature recurring motif – the crown – the artist recognizes the majesty of his heroes: groundbreaking athletes, musicians and writers.
fields.side_note: Fits standard A3 frames. Frame is not included.

fields.name: Self Portrait Print
fields.description: Basquiat is a famous painter known for his raw gestural style of painting with graffiti-like images and scrawled text.With his signature recurring motif – the crown – the artist recognizes the majesty of his heroes: groundbreaking athletes, musicians and writers.

fields.name: Glowing Pumpkin Print
fields.description: Yayoi Kasuma is a very famous Japanese artist, infamous for her 'dotted' works. Her work with dots can be read as a means of therapy, of confronting a fear by representing it on a grand scale.
fields.side_note: Fits standard A3 frames. Frame is not included.

fields.name: Fan Work Print
fields.description: This is a fun fan work print of Yayoi Kasuma immersed in a world of dots, pumpkins and her magical paint brushes.
fields.side_note: Fits standard A3 frames. Frame is not included.
